Class GameWindowImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.WindowAbstract
      • view.game.GameWindowImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameWindow, Window

    public final class GameWindowImpl
extends WindowAbstract
implements GameWindow
    An implementation of GameWindow. It uses a GameCanvas object to manage the canvas drawings.
